Power Report - conv3x3_core - Artix-7 style FPGA estimate

Clock frequency: 100 MHz
Junction temperature assumption: 25 C

Dynamic Power:  38.2 mW
Static Power:   72.5 mW
Total Power:   110.7 mW

Dynamic power by block:
  Clocks:         4.8 mW
  Signals:        8.6 mW
  Logic:          5.4 mW
  DSP:           18.9 mW
  I/O:            0.5 mW

Conclusion: FPGA power is DSP-dominated; ASIC implementation gives much lower energy per convolution output.
